elements.name: User can login to the application with valid credentials and purchase the specific men's jacket.

steps.name: User already logged in the application and verify the user information on the landing page
User should be able to select jacket from men module
Verify the jacket name on the "Jupiter All-Weather Trainer" list
User should be able to select the "S" and "Blue" and "1" then click on the add to cart
User should be able to click on the cart
User should be able to click on the checkout
